Class LevelXMLReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • utilities.LevelXMLReader

  • public class LevelXMLReader
extends java.lang.Object
    LevelXMLReader is used to parse an XML file following the LevelsXMLSchema.xsd into a GameLevel.
    Author:
    Jan Nylen, Alexander Ekstrom
